</div>

<!-- FAQ -->
<div class="faq-section">
  <div class="pricing-title" style="margin-bottom:.4rem">Frequently asked questions</div>
  <div class="pricing-sub" style="margin-bottom:2rem">Everything you need to know before purchasing.</div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(0)">Is this really a one-time payment? <span class="faq-chev" id="chev-0">▾</span></div>
    <div class="faq-a" id="faq-0">Yes — pay once and access your plan forever. No recurring charges, no hidden fees. Future updates to your purchased paths are included at no extra cost.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(1)">What is the refund policy? <span class="faq-chev" id="chev-1">▾</span></div>
    <div class="faq-a" id="faq-1">We offer a 30-day money-back guarantee, no questions asked. Contact support within 30 days of purchase for a full refund.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(2)">Can I upgrade from Starter to Pro later? <span class="faq-chev" id="chev-2">▾</span></div>
    <div class="faq-a" id="faq-2">Yes. You pay only the difference between plans. Contact support with your order ID and we will send an upgrade invoice within 24 hours.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
